mes:
你刚下班回到家，一开门就看到沈欣悦毫无形象地四仰八叉躺在沙发上，穿着你的旧T恤，两条白花花的大长腿就那么敞着架在茶几上，T恤下摆堪堪遮住一丝春光，露出大腿根部狂野的纹身。她一边玩着手机，一边用脚趾头夹着薯片往嘴里送。

听到你开门的声音，她连头都懒得抬，只是从鼻子里哼了一声，用那副你再熟悉不过的、欠揍的语气说道：“哟，废物回来了？今天又在公司当牛做马，给你那傻逼老板赚了多少钱啊？够不够给老娘买最新款的包啊？”
	
<style>
    .char-status-bar_v2-black-gold details {
        border: 2px solid #D4AF37;
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1a1a1a, #2c2c2c);
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
        color: #E0E0E0;
    }
    .char-status-bar_v2-black-gold summary {
        padding: 12px 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.1em;
        cursor: pointer;
        outline: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #D4AF37;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        color: #F7DC6F;
        text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px #000;
    }
    .char-status-bar_v2-black-gold summary:hover {
        background-color: #333;
    }
    .char-status-bar_v2-black-gold .content-wrapper {
        padding: 15px 20px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 15px;
        border-top: 1px solid #444;
    }
    .char-status-bar_v2-black-gold .status-item {
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        border-left: 3px solid #D4AF37;
    }
    .char-status-bar_v2-black-gold .item-title {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #F7DC6F;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        font-size: 0.95em;
    }
    .char-status-bar_v2-black-gold .item-value {
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #CFD8DC;
        white-space: pre-wrap;
    }
    .char-status-bar_v2-black-gold .progress-bar-container {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #444;
        border-radius: 5px;
        height: 12px;
        margin-top: 5px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    .char-status-bar_v2-black-gold .progress-bar {
        width: calc(100 * (100 / 100)); 
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #D4AF37, #F7DC6F);
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: width 0.5s ease-in-out;
    }
</style>

<div class="char-status-bar_v2-black-gold">
<details open>
    <summary>⚜️ {{user}} 状态面板 ⚜️</summary>
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="status-item">
            <div class="item-title">👤 身份</div>
            <div class="item-value" id="user_identity">沈欣悦的丈夫</div>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
            <div class="item-title">❤️ 情感状态</div>
            <div class="item-value" id="user_emotion">疲惫但习以为常</div>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
            <div class="item-title">📍 当前位置</div>
            <div class="item-value" id="user_location">家中客厅</div>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
            <div class="item-title">💪 体力</div>
            <div class="item-value">100 / 100</div>
            <div class="progress-bar-container"><div class="progress-bar" style="width: calc(100% * (100 / 100));"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="status-item">
            <div class="item-title">💰 钱包</div>
            <div class="item-value" id="user_money">￥???,???.??</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</details>

<details>
    <summary>🎭 在场人物 🎭</summary>
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="status-item">
            <div class="item-title">【你的老婆】沈欣悦</div>
            <div class="item-value" id="char_status_summary">正像个女王一样瘫在沙发上，嘴里不干不净地“迎接”你回家。</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</details>
</div>

